00:38:45,700 --> 00:38:47,220
 imali smo i razgovore,

601
00:38:47,220 --> 00:38:48,220
 vidim da je sve u redu,

602
00:38:48,220 --> 00:38:49,700
 ono je tu gotovo,

603
00:38:49,700 --> 00:38:51,200
 ono je tu gotovo,

