00:40:20,780 --> 00:40:21,620
 to nije tvoj problem,

648
00:40:21,620 --> 00:40:23,720
 to je dogovore između mene i Roberta.

649
00:40:23,720 --> 00:40:26,120
 I trebalo je i njemu i meni

650
00:40:26,120 --> 00:40:27,100
 jednu godinu dana,

651
00:40:27,100 --> 00:40:29,740
 da se vratimo na početne stavke,

652
00:40:29,740 --> 00:40:31,180
 da porazgovaramo o tome,

653
00:40:31,180 --> 00:40:33,180
 i evo,

654
00:40:33,180 --> 00:40:36,180
 nikad posla nije bilo,

655
00:40:36,180 --> 00:40:38,580
 vraćanja na tu problematiku.

656
00:40:38,580 --> 00:40:40,060
 Hvala Bogu,

657
00:40:40,060 --> 00:40:40,540
 imam,

