663
00:40:53,880 --> 00:40:54,660
 I to veliko,

664
00:40:54,660 --> 00:40:55,720
 to ne možeš ni samisliti,

665
00:40:55,720 --> 00:40:57,380
 samisli da si ti sad dužan nekome

666
00:40:57,380 --> 00:40:58,560
 i skoro osta,

667
00:40:58,560 --> 00:41:00,180
 ovo me ostane beskuće skoro,

668
00:41:00,180 --> 00:41:02,280
 oni su ostali beskuće,

669
00:41:03,080 --> 00:41:04,640
