675
00:41:13,240 --> 00:41:14,640
 ova je vamo patla,

676
00:41:14,640 --> 00:41:16,620
 ti to si,

677
00:41:16,620 --> 00:41:19,100
 a u drugom trenutku ti daje snagu da to nosiš.

678
00:41:21,280 --> 00:41:23,120
 To je stvarno tako bilo.

679
00:41:23,120 --> 00:41:23,960
 To je stvarno,

680
00:41:23,960 --> 00:41:26,960
 ja ničem to drugom ne mogu prepisati,

681
00:41:26,960 --> 00:41:28,200
