685
00:41:34,280 --> 00:41:36,040
 I zato uvijek naglašavan.

686
00:41:36,040 --> 00:41:39,000
 Neće Bog ti dat novce,

687
00:41:39,000 --> 00:41:42,340
 neće ti Bog dat rješenje na papiru,

