00:41:52,780 --> 00:41:53,720
 da bi došao do cilja.

692
00:41:53,720 --> 00:41:56,100
 I bez križa nema cilja.

693
00:41:56,100 --> 00:41:56,940
 Nema!

694
00:41:56,940 --> 00:41:58,840
 Nama je treba veliki

695
00:41:58,840 --> 00:42:00,400
