708
00:42:23,200 --> 00:42:25,340
 Ica objašnjavala veljeni.

709
00:42:25,340 --> 00:42:26,760
 Zašto?

710
00:42:26,760 --> 00:42:28,560
 Jednostavno, manje posla,

711
00:42:28,560 --> 00:42:29,480
 malo smiri vaš.

712
00:42:29,480 --> 00:42:32,400
 I tako da su i oni u toj poniznosti rezli.

713
00:42:32,400 --> 00:42:33,780
 Sve do jedno, dite.

714
00:42:33,860 --> 00:42:35,140
 Hvala Bogu.

715
00:42:35,140 --> 00:42:37,000
 A ja sam,

716
00:42:37,000 --> 00:42:38,340
 evo,

717
00:42:38,340 --> 00:42:40,880
