718
00:42:40,880 --> 00:42:42,780
 da prihvati,

719
00:42:42,780 --> 00:42:44,280
 jer nije tribalo pomoć.

720
00:42:44,280 --> 00:42:46,300
 Ja sam tribala ostati normalna,

721
00:42:46,300 --> 00:42:48,280
 jer tu je bilo došla granica

722
00:42:48,280 --> 00:42:50,920
 ili ćeš poludit

723
00:42:50,920 --> 00:42:52,860
 i uništit

724
00:42:52,860 --> 00:42:53,820
 dicu

725
00:42:53,820 --> 00:42:56,700
 i naravno još gore napravitnik je

726
00:42:56,700 --> 00:42:58,600
 ili ćeš sisti i moli, pa šta god bude,

727
00:42:58,600 --> 00:43:01,060
 šta god da se desi prihvatit ću.

728
00:43:01,060 --> 00:43:03,060
 Znači, šta god da je se desilo.

729
00:43:03,060 --> 00:43:03,660
 Da ne znam,

730
00:43:03,660 --> 00:43:05,640
 da me dođu upucati,

731
00:43:05,640 --> 00:43:07,840
 da ne znam s čim ja to objasnam.

732
00:43:08,620 --> 00:43:10,160
 Nema šanse da popustim.

733
00:43:10,160 --> 00:43:11,300
 Dođe ti u trenutka,

734
00:43:11,300 --> 00:43:12,460
