735
00:43:12,460 --> 00:43:13,260
 Bože, ima u te.

736
00:43:13,260 --> 00:43:15,580
 I znaš šta sam onda rekla?

737
00:43:15,580 --> 00:43:17,600
 Ja, onaj,

738
00:43:17,600 --> 00:43:19,840
 zauzinat ću vjerovat u tebe.

739
00:43:19,840 --> 00:43:21,080
 Zauzinat.

740
00:43:21,080 --> 00:43:21,940
 Šta god da se desi?

741
00:43:21,940 --> 00:43:23,080
 Ja ću zauzinat,

742
