770
00:44:20,600 --> 00:44:23,320
 To će posebno matere shvatiti.

771
00:44:23,320 --> 00:44:26,700
 Da li su one sposobne odbaciti svoje dide?

772
00:44:27,120 --> 00:44:28,540
 Evo, ne znam,

773
00:44:28,540 --> 00:44:31,260
