774
00:44:31,260 --> 00:44:32,340
 Da li su?

775
00:44:32,340 --> 00:44:34,980
 Znači, čin je problematično,

776
00:44:34,980 --> 00:44:37,780
 čin je nešto na njem nije u redu,

777
00:44:37,780 --> 00:44:40,500
 čin, ili su mu oči križaste,

778
00:44:40,500 --> 00:44:41,700
 ili ima problem,

779
00:44:41,700 --> 00:44:43,640
 ili nismo zadovoljni s to.

780
00:44:43,640 --> 00:44:44,400
 I to treba baje.

781
00:44:44,400 --> 00:44:45,020
 Ko mačiće?

782
00:44:46,020 --> 00:44:48,600
 Teško je zato što danas se brakne svoća ozbiljno.

783
00:44:48,600 --> 00:44:53,180
 I smatram da zvi zapovedi ljubavi se stvarno treba držati.

784
00:44:53,180 --> 00:44:54,720
 Ne znam kakvi smo mi to ljudi.

785
00:44:54,720 --> 00:44:56,980
 Dok iđe dobro, dok imamo novica, sve u redu.

786
00:44:56,980 --> 00:44:59,160
 Ajmo se volt kad nemamo.

787
00:44:59,160 --> 00:45:02,100
 Ajmo vidjet koliko smo ljudi.

788
00:45:02,100 --> 00:45:05,000
 Ajmo vidjet koliko moramo to.

789
00:45:05,160 --> 00:45:06,420
 Lako je dobro biti vjer.

790
00:45:06,420 --> 00:45:08,280
 Ajmo pa, u tome je stvar.

791
00:45:08,280 --> 00:45:11,380
 Nema života bez križa.

792
00:45:11,380 --> 00:45:13,940
 Koliko goto, oni zamišljali da je sve idealno,

793
00:45:13,940 --> 00:45:16,240
 harmonično, imamo dobro auto,

794
00:45:16,240 --> 00:45:17,280
 imamo dobru kuću,

795
00:45:17,280 --> 00:45:19,440
 ali to je križ.

796
00:45:19,440 --> 00:45:20,840
 Kakav takav, možda ne ovi,

797
00:45:20,840 --> 00:45:23,860
 možda neki drugi šteta

798
00:45:23,860 --> 00:45:25,580
 da se obitelji, posebno mlade,

799
00:45:25,580 --> 00:45:27,200
